Membership
We invite you to learn more about Lexington Oaks Golf Club, its members, and its traditions. The best time to become a member is right now. Enjoy time with family and friends, play golf or unwind over dinner and drinks. Reward yourself with a Lexington Oaks Golf Club membership. You will feel right at home.
Interested in joining our club? Please call 813 907-7270.

Tournaments
Lexington Oaks Golf Club provides golf tournament services to the golf, charity and business communities in the greater Tampa area. Lexington Oaks offerings are founded on the premise that golf related services should be provided in a professional, business-like manner.
Charities and businesses view golf tournaments as a positive method to raise funds or reward employees and customers in a relaxed and fun setting. The event must be successful for all involved parties. However, your organization does not have as its primary focus the planning and execution of such events. That is where the staff at Lexington Oaks comes in. We facilitate all the details of your tournament while maintaining the focus on your desired result.
Lexington Oaks golf tournament services cover all facets of planning, organizing and operating golf tournaments and related activities. Charity and corporate services we provide include:
Tournament or clinic theme development
Communications planning and execution
Tournament registration, operations and post tournament follow-ups
On course services such as proximity contests, hole in one and photography
Selection of prizes, tee bags, favors and trophies
Food and beverage coordination
Lexington Oaks specializes in planning and executing tournaments, outings and leagues. We will be creative and innovative in our approach to facilitate the perfect event for you, your company or charity. The staff at Lexington Oaks has the experience to handle every detail for you. Based on your goals and services that you need, we will customize a detailed proposal for you, outlining every service and detail of the tournament planning process.
If you would like to find out more about what Lexington Oaks has to offer you, please call the Pro Shop 813-907-7270.
